Description: The Dean Deceiver X Electric Guitar's single-cutaway mahogany body is crafted with a C-profile, bolt-on maple neck. The guitar's 24-fret rosewood fingerboard is decorated with cool pearl Deceiver inlays. The Deceiver X has a traditional 25½" scale length and a 3-on-the-side Dean headstock design with a winged Dean logo. High-output humbucking pickups deliver a variety of rockin' tones. The Deceiver's black-nickel hardware includes a Tune-o-matic-style bridge with a string-thru-body tail for added sustain.
